@Land\_comment  
He can't kill [Arcades Sabboth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Arcades Sabboth), unless they throw in extra blockers for no reason. He trades off one-for-one for the others.  
Rampage only triggers for each blocker beyond the first. If they block with one creature he gets no bonus, if they block with 3 he gets +4/+4.

